query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get all Stock Out records
  ดึงรายการเบิกสินค้าออกจากคลังทั้งหมดของหน่วยธุรกิจ พร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและตัวกรอง ใช้สำหรับผู้จัดการคลังสินค้าในการติดตามการเบิกจ่ายสินค้าไปยังครัวและแผนกต่างๆ

  Lists all inventory removal records for the business unit with pagination and filtering. Used by inventory managers to track consumption by kitchens and departments, monitor waste levels, and analyze usage patterns.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `page` | number | No | 1 | Page number |
  | `perpage` | number | No | 10 | Items per page |
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `inventory_management.stock_out:view`
  - **Roles**: HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "so_no": "SO-2026-0001",
        "so_date": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
        "description": "Kitchen daily consumption",
        "doc_status": "draft",
        "location_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "location_name": "Main Store",
        "item_count": 3,
        "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 5,
      "total": 48,
      "prev": null,
      "next": 2
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `inventory_management.stock_out:view` permission |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}
